---
title: Crumbed Pumpkin Wedges with Herbs & Parmesan | Serves 2
description: We've worked out how to improve the classic side dish of golden roasted pumpkin wedges—add a crunchy topping of panko
breadcrumbs, garlic, herbs and Parmesan! Trust us, once you've tried this jazzed-up version there's no going back.
